snippet.title: Star Wars Old Republic: Trailer (E3 2011)
snippet.description:
Which side will you chose in the new MMORPG Star Wars Old Republic? Watch the epic battle between the Jedi and the Sith in this E3 2011 trailer!

Subscribe to IGN's The Old Republic channel so you don't miss out on any of our videos:
http://www.youtube.com/oldrepublicign
 
For more info on The Old Republic, do a barrel roll and head over to IGN:
http://pc.ign.com/objects/816/816935.html
